Guangxi college students can suspend their business for up to 5 years-Xinhuanet Xinhua Agency Nanning May 19 th(Reporter Zhang Ying) Reporters recently learned from the Guangxi Zhuang Autonomous Region Department of Education that in the future, universities in Guangxi will implement a flexible school system and relax the length of time for college students to suspend their studies. The length of time for college students to suspend their studies and start their own businesses can be extended by 2 to 5 years on the basis of the original school system. The time for suspending their studies and starting their own businesses can be regarded as practical education time. In order to promote the improvement of college students 'entrepreneurial and innovative ability, Guangxi Education, Human Resources and Social Security and other departments have joined forces to build an entrepreneurial platform and build more off-campus practical teaching bases for college students, university science parks,College students 'entrepreneurship parks and business incubation bases provide external guarantee for college students' entrepreneurship. According to the requirements, by 2020, the area of innovation and entrepreneurship practice bases in colleges and universities should reach more than 3000 square meters for undergraduate schools and more than 2000 square meters for higher vocational schools. The government encourages colleges and universities to set up innovation and entrepreneurship credits and give priority to supporting students who have performed well in innovation and entrepreneurship practice to transfer to majors. College teachers every two years to have at least two months to the industry enterprise temporary exercise, In order to improve the awareness and ability of teachers innovation and entrepreneurship education. Autonomous region education department requires guangxi colleges and universities to implement the innovation and entrepreneurship training program, Strive to make every college student during the school to participate in an innovation and entrepreneurship training program. Colleges and universities should actively organize students to participate in all kinds of innovation and entrepreneurship competition, And give financial support.
